        on X/Twitter to verify ownership of the GitHub handle. We’ll honour removal requests. If blocked, reach out via another
        channel — verification is still supported.
      </dd>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Can I <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-cyan-600 to-emerald-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent dark:from-blue-400 dark:via-cyan-400 dark:to-emerald-400 animate-gradient">opt out</span> permanently?</dt>
      <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        Yes. Opt‑out is permanent unless you explicitly request removal. We will never add your profile without consent after opt‑out.
      </dd>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">What do I get with my <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-cyan-600 to-emerald-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent dark:from-blue-400 dark:via-cyan-400 dark:to-emerald-400 animate-gradient">TecHub profile</span>?</dt>
      <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Sharable profile with optional Cards/OG images.</li>
          <li>Searchable directory placement with tags, archetypes, and spirit animals.</li>
          <li>JSON API access to the same data.</li>
          <li>Configurable via repo or UI.</li>
        </ul>
      </dd>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">How can I <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-cyan-600 to-emerald-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent dark:from-blue-400 dark:via-cyan-400 dark:to-emerald-400 animate-gradient">use</span> my card?</dt>
      <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><span class="font-semibold">Flex:</span> add it to your README, portfolio, and bio.</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold">Discover:</span> explore builders by languages, stacks, vibes, and styles.</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold">Build:</span> use the JSON for leaderboards, trend graphs, or integrations.</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold">Support:</span> card developers you rate to help them join the collection.</li>
        </ul>
      </dd>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Where can I find images and <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-cyan-600 to-emerald-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent dark:from-blue-400 dark:via-cyan-400 dark:to-emerald-400 animate-gradient">JSON</span>?</dt>
      <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        JSON: <code class="whitespace-nowrap">/profiles/:username.json</code> • OG image: <code class="whitespace-nowrap">/og/:login.jpg</code>. If missing, generation is queued automatically.
      </dd>
