    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-4 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">What permissions does TecHub request?</dt>
      <dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-2">
        <p><span class="font-semibold">Minimal scopes:</span> we request only <code>read:user</code> for your basic GitHub profile. We do <span class="font-semibold">not</span> request your email or private repo access.</p>
